content.task: Quality assurance strategy for Enterprise Features Phase 2 integration. Define comprehensive testing approach for Trading tier integration including test coverage requirements, validation criteria, and quality gates for liquidity management and yield farming features. Ensure compliance with DEVELOPMENT_RULES.md requirement: NEVER SKIP FAILING TESTS.
content.context: Phase 1 achieved 100% test success rate (8/8 tests passing). Phase 2 will integrate complex trading algorithms: stellar_liquidity_management.py with AMM pool management, arbitrage detection, and risk assessment capabilities; stellar_yield_farming.py with DeFi protocol integration and yield optimization strategies. Testing must validate both individual components and integration with existing enterprise framework.
